      "description": "A vulnerability has been found in D-Link DNS-120, DNR-202L, DNS-315L, DNS-320, DNS-320L, DNS-320LW, DNS-321, DNR-322L, DNS-323, DNS-325, DNS-326, DNS-327L, DNR-326, DNS-340L, DNS-343, DNS-345, DNS-726-4, DNS-1100-4, DNS-1200-05 and DNS-1550-04 up to 20260205. This impacts the function cgi_recovery/cgi_backup_now/cgi_set_schedule/cgi_set_rsync_server of the file /cgi-bin/remote_backup.cgi. The manipulation leads to command injection. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.",
